########################
NagminVX4 ChangeLog
########################

!!!!!!!!! Download now from NagminVX_CI_4.5.3 branch !!!!!!!!!

20250107
---------
- if you try to store it will now checked if field allow NULL
- table changes: Host: alias DEFAULT NULL (
ALTER TABLE `Host` 
CHANGE `alias` `alias` varchar(80) COLLATE 'utf8mb3_general_ci' NULL DEFAULT '' AFTER `host_name`;)
ALTER TABLE `Command`
CHANGE `command_line` `command_line` text COLLATE 'utf8mb3_general_ci' NOT NULL AFTER `command_name`;

20240818
---------
- Configs Table: Tools ; Important! now using row action (not name) for to control what happens. As a side effect, the name can also contain spaces.
as default action the table or view will displayed

20240804
---------
- 	CI_VERSION 4.5.3
- recommend: https://forum.codeigniter.com/showthread.php?tid=86130 
